<strong>BIBLIOGRAPHY ENTRY</strong>
<br><br>
Add a bibliography at the end of your essay citing all relevant sources used in your research, regardless of whether they are explicitly mentioned in your writing.
<br><br>
An electronic article retrieved from a database uses the same format as a printed journal article 
with the addition of a Digital Object Identifier (DOI). The <a href="http://www.crossref.org/guestquery" title="CrossRef &#45; Look up DOIs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI resolver</a> can be used to find a DOI from the citation details if it is not given in the publication. If a DOI is available, include it at the end of the reference as a URL e.g. https://doi.org/10.1080/10.1201/b15592. If no DOI is available, provide the name of the database or a <a href="%%ICiteBasePath%%guides/using-library-resources" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stable URL</a>. Many databases have options to create stable URLs &mdash; look for terms like &#8216;Permalink&#8217;, &#8216;Bookmark URL&#8217;, &#8216;Embed/Link&#8217; or &#8216;Stable URL&#8217;.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	Author&#8217;s surname, given name. &#34;Title of Article.&#34; <em>Journal Title</em> volume, no. issue (year): pages. https://doi.org/Digital object identifier number.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	<span class="hover" title="Author&#8217;s surname, given name">Smith, Alex, and Bridget Brown</span>. 
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of Article">Dining Out: A History of Restaurant Eating in New Zealand</span>.&#34; 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Journal Title">Journal of New Zealand Historical Research</span></em> 
	<span class="hover" title="volume">10</span>, 
	no. <span class="hover" title="issue">2</span> 
	(<span class="hover" title="year">2056</span>): 
	<span class="hover" title="pages">110&#45;123</span>. 
	https://doi.org/<span class="hover" title="Digital object identifier">10.1108/13522750710740855</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
