<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br><br>
Put a footnote number in your text to show when you are using another person&#8217;s ideas or words.
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	&#34;Restaurant dining was an important aspect of tourism in nineteenth century New Zealand&#34;.
	<sup>1</sup>
</blockquote>
<br>
This number directs your reader to a footnote at the bottom of your page. The footnote contains detailed information about the work you are citing.
<br><br>
<strong>FOOTNOTES</strong>
<br><br>
If individual page numbers are not available, you may describe where the material was found by 
giving the relevant subheading, after the word &#8216;under&#8217; (Example B). Otherwise, use the
standard form for footnotes, omitting page numbers.
<br><br>
When references to the same work follow each other with no other references in&#45;between, use a shortened citation in the first instance (Example C). If other references to the same article follow directly after, replace the author&#8217;s name and title with <strong>ibid</strong> (Example D) and the page number if it differs from the previous citation.
<br><br>
<strong>Example A &#45; page number provided</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">1. Aroha Upton and Bridget Brown, &#34;Dining Out: A History of Restaurant Eating in New Zealand,&#34; <em>Journal of New Zealand Historical Research</em> 10, no. 2 (2056): 110&#45;123, https://doi.org/10.1108/13522750710740855.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example B &#45; subheading provided</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">7. Alex Smith and Bridget Brown, &#34;Dining Out: A History of Restaurant Eating in New Zealand,&#34; <em>Journal of New Zealand Historical Research</em> 10, no. 2 (2056), under &#34;Introduction&#34;, https://doi.org/10.1108/13522750710740855.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example C</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">8. Smith and Brown, &#34;Dining Out,&#34; 115.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example D</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">9. Ibid.</span>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example E</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="footnotes ref-indent-1-27cm">
	<span class="smaller">10. Ibid., 118</span>
</blockquote>
